cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SE 

This paper deals with controller synthesis for cyber-physical systems, which involves the integration of computer systems and physical processes. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with the synthesis of safe controllers, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SE (Software Engineering).
